The paper deals with the performance analysis of joint channel estimation, multiuser detection, and per-user decoding for MIMO DS-CDMA systems. This involves the use of statistical mechanics and the replica method to evaluate the performance in the large-system limit. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.COM (Computers and Society).
